title: 820-3462-A - A1425 - Won't charge and running Slow
message: Run EFI ASD to check for sensor errors. Is battery recognized in OSX and is the condition reported as "normal"

title: 820-3462-A - A1425 - Won't charge and running Slow
820-3462-A - A1425 - Won't charge and running Slow
message: TW0p airport sensor is mounted on IO board. So either bad cable or corrosion on connectors.
